channel.title: I have a prob with my scripts
channel.description:
I got these 4 scripts from kaitneiks and now i am trying to re-use them & i keep getting these errors:
ultimate chop 3.0v: Line 826: [Error] (5677:8): Unknown identifier 'FindEnt' in script C:\Documents and Settings\David\Desktop\ultimate chop 3.0v.scar
Stupid's scripts: Line 68: [Error] (4570:1): Unknown identifier 'ScarScape' in script C:\Documents and Settings\David\Desktop\fally guildminerbaner.scar
Line 64: [Error] (4566:1): Unknown identifier 'ScarScape' in script C:\Documents and Settings\David\Desktop\stupids powerminer.scar
Moparsironminerbanker: Line 47: [Error] (4968:1): Unknown identifier 'ScarScape' in script C:\Documents and Settings\David\Desktop\moparsironminerbanker.scar
They are the errors i am getting...i paid 500k for the ultimate chop so you know how angry i am at that for not working. But i keep on getting these errors on those scripts....plz help me casue i really want them to work. I got all the include's for everyone but it just won't seem to work, just those errors!!
Thanks for the help. vader killer
